title: Lol in a nutshell.

embed.description: A League of Legends parody of the song "We're Going to be Friends" by The White Stripes. Download this song at: http://nevercake.newgrounds.com Lyrics: ---------------- Start the game, sit in queue I can't wait to kill some noobs Loading screen, here we go Our team comp is super-pro Look at all our skins, We're going to win I can't wait for the fun to begin.

body: a videó nem az enyém, de gondoltam megosztom mert nagyon deep.
